appearance.text: has elaborately braided hair or beard
has a holy symbol branded onto hand

motivation.text: To succeed, to become the best
To make money and buy things
To be cherished, admired, and wanted
To make peace, to create balance
To create, build or invent things
To get married, have children, and live a family life
To find honor through battle or self-sacrifice
To exalt ideals such as generosity, honesty, bravery, and courtliness
To arrange, organize, and reduce chaos
To have fun, to enjoy life
To spread a belief system and indoctrinate others
To achieve a state of moral or spiritual perfection
To follow a person, government, order, or religion
To inflict pain and suffering, on others and/or the self
To seek knowledge or wisdom (spiritual, scientific, or magical)
To enable or engage in self-destructive behavior
